      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, dry, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium-low heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>cashew nuts</strong> and cook for 3-4 min, or until they've darkened slightly in colour</p><p>Tip: Watch them like a hawk to make sure they don't burn!</p><p>Once done, set them aside to cool slightly and save the pan for later</p>",
