    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Top, tail, peel and finely dice your <strong>carrot[s]</strong></p><p>Top, tail and finely dice your <strong>courgette[s]</strong></p><p>Slice your<strong> chestnut mushrooms</strong> finely</p>",
