    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the pan to a medium heat with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>diced carrot</strong>, <strong>diced courgette</strong>,<strong> sliced onion</strong>,<strong> sliced mushrooms</strong> and <strong>half</strong> of the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>garlic </strong>(save the rest for later!) with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Cook for 10-15 min or until everything is starting to caramelise</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
