    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add your<strong> wholewheat noodles</strong> to a large bowl, cover them with <strong>boiled water</strong> and stir for 10 secs to separate the noodles</p><p>Set aside to soak for 4 min</p><p>Drain the <strong>soaked noodles</strong>, reserving a cup of the <strong>starchy noodle water</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/472.step-5-x200.jpg",
