        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your<strong> coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks, then chop the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>cashew nuts</strong> coarsely</p><p>Cut your <strong>red</strong> <strong>chilli[es]</strong> in half lengthways, deseed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon) and chop finely</p><p>Once the vegetables have caramelised, add the <strong>drained noodles</strong> with the <strong>silky cashew nut sauce</strong>, <strong>soy sauce</strong> and <strong>half</strong> the <strong>chopped coriander</strong> (save the rest for garnish!) – these are your <strong>vegetable noodles with silky cashew nut sauce</strong></p>",
