      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>vegetable noodles with silky cashew nut sauce</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining chopped cashew nuts</strong>, <strong>reserved chopped coriander</strong> and the <strong>chopped chilli </strong>(can’t handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
